      "para_id": "Q004990.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Ibbi-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Nanna-ludug , the scribe , child of Lu-diĝira , is your servant ."
    }
  ],
